{"title":"[图论]构造完全图","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1099#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=1099","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1099/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1099/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/1099"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于完全图G,若有且仅有一棵最小生成树为T，则称完全图G是树T的扩展出的。给你一\r\n棵树T,找出T能扩展出的边权和最小的完全图G。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行N表示树T的点数。\r\n接下来N-1行： Si， Ti， Di；描述一条边（ Si,Ti）权值为 Di。\r\n保证输入数据构成一棵树。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一个数，表示最小的图G的边权和。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"```\r\n样例输入\r\n4\r\n1 2 1\r\n1 3 1\r\n1 4 2\r\n```\r\n```\r\n样例输出\r\n12\r\n```\r\n样例说明\r\n添加D(2,3)=2,D(3,4)=3,D(2,4)=3即可。"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于20%的数据， N<=10\r\n对于50%的数据， N<=1000\r\n对于100%的数据， N<=100000， 1<=Di<=100000"}]}